    "Subsequently, we search for the movie reviewers based on a pre-specified metastructure ( MS = U → M → C&&T → M → U).",
    "As illus- trated in Fig. 1, it depicts an instance of the meta-structure marked by dotted contour lines.",
    "The meta-structure pattern u 1 → m 1 → c&&t 1 → m 2 → u 3 is an example, where we can add u 3, along with other potential reviewers, to the candidate reviewer list that complies with this meta-structure pattern.",
